Script original by Felipe N. Moura (@felipenmoura), adapted to run on OpenSUSE distro
by Cauan Cabral (@cauancabral).

You should run it as it follows:
  sudo sh ./PDEB.sh

Then, just answer the questions.
The last step would be setting the permissions to your server, like this:
sudo chmod 777 -R /srv/www/htdocs

well...the 777 is up to you ;)
